---
import PublicLayout from '../../layouts/PublicLayout.astro';
---

<PublicLayout
  title="Consultancy and Facilitation"
  description="Hands-on agile consultancy and facilitation. We work alongside your teams to help them deliver better outcomes."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 sm:py-20">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-grey-900 dark:text-white">
      Consultancy and Facilitation
    </h1>

    <div class="mt-8 prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p class="text-xl text-grey-700 dark:text-grey-300">
        Your teams are doing agile, but something is not clicking. Ceremonies feel like box-ticking.
        Delivery is unpredictable. People are frustrated.
      </p>

      <h2>What we do</h2>
      <p>
        We embed alongside your teams to understand what is really happening. Not from a
        textbook perspective, but from the reality of your people, your culture, and your goals.
      </p>
      <p>We help with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Identifying and addressing systemic impediments to flow</li>
        <li>Facilitating retrospectives, workshops, and planning sessions</li>
        <li>Coaching teams and individuals through agile adoption and improvement</li>
        <li>Supporting leadership in creating the conditions for agile to thrive</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How we work</h2>
      <p>
        We are remote-first, which means we are set up to work effectively with distributed teams.
        Engagements can be short-term (a focused sprint of improvement) or longer-term
        (ongoing partnership as your teams grow in maturity).
      </p>

      <h2>Get started</h2>
      <p>
        <a href="/contact/">Book a free consultation call</a> to discuss your challenges.
        No obligation, no sales pitch. Just an honest conversation about how we might help.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</PublicLayout>
